name: Approaching Summit
description:
This is one of my first notable images as a photographer after starting in 2006. It has been featured in exhibitions, print, and television, and it still holds a special place in my heart until today. I felt absolutely exhausted at the time, as I was not really used to climbing mountains. But as we approached the summit of Mt. Gulugod Baboy, this scene unfolded in front of me and I was suddenly re-energized, taking photos until the sun went down.

Batangas, Philippines 2007
